data.description: Full Golf Membership Available!! Experience luxury living in Naples' prestigious Greyhawk community. This exceptional 2021-built single-family home offers full golf membership eligibility. The open-concept design of this 4-bedroom home, featuring 2 dens and 3 full bathrooms, creates a spacious and inviting atmosphere. The chef's kitchen is a culinary dream, equipped with upgraded stainless-steel appliances, including a beverage cooler and a large island that connects seamlessly to the great room and dining area. Uniting indoor and outdoor living, the zero-corner sliders lead you to the covered outdoor living space, where a custom heated pool awaits within an expanded screened lanai. The master bedroom showcases a tray ceiling and a spa-like ensuite bathroom with two large walk-in closets. Three spacious guest bedrooms and two additional full baths ensure ample space for family and guests. Greyhawk's world-class amenities include a spectacular resort-style pool and spa, a full-service restaurant, and an outdoor bar and grill. Engage in friendly competition on the tennis and pickleball courts, stay active in the fitness center, or enjoy a leisurely game of bocce ball.
